## Revenue Model

Astra generates revenue through:

### FX Conversion

Fees on USDC-to-local-currency conversions.

### Cross-Border Payments

Transaction fees on international business payments.

### Treasury Services

Premium treasury, reporting, and financial management tools.

### Subscription Plans

Advanced business accounts and team features.

### API Access

Infrastructure services for fintechs, marketplaces, and platforms.

